4. 적합

set(df_train.columns) - set(df_test.columns)
{'SalePrice'}
# step1 -- pass
# step2
predictr = TabularPredictor(label='SalePrice')
# step3
predictr.fit(df_train)
# step4
yhat = predictr.predict(df_train)
yyhat = predictr.predict(df_test)
